The paper discusses sentiment analysis and ranking of scientific papers, which are topics that are commonly studied in the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-categories of arXiv CS. However, since the paper focuses on sentiment analysis and ranking of scientific papers, cs.IR and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories, followed by cs.AI, cs.LG, and cs.SI.
